@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_cahnnm(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (((v0 + 0.03 + v1 + 0.07) + wp.sin(v0 + 0.61)) + (wp.cos(tmp + 0.99) / (v0 + 0.95 - tmp + 0.37)))
    v2 = (wp.cos(v2) * v0)
    tmp = (wp.cos(0.42) * wp.abs((tmp + 0.93 + v0 + 0.71)))
    data[tid] = v0
